OL,3,CHouseholds urged to send in meter
OL,4,Creadings ahead of Oct 1 price hike
OL,6,FThe regulator has raised the cap from
OL,7,Fthe current #1,568 for a typical dual
OL,8,Ffuel household in England, Scotland
OL,9,Fand Wales to #1,717, or around #12 a
OL,10,Fmonth more on an average bills.
OL,12,FThe latest cap will be just 6% or #117
OL,13,Flower than it was compared to the same
OL,14,Fperiod last year.
