OL,3,CHouseholds urged to send in meter
OL,4,Creadings ahead of Oct 1 price hike
OL,6,FFor gas, the average will be 6.24p per
OL,7,Funit with a standing charge of 31.66p
OL,8,Fper day.
OL,10,FOfgem said rising prices in the
OL,11,Finternational energy market, due to
OL,12,Fheightened political tensions and
OL,13,Fextreme weather events, were the main
OL,14,Fdriver behind the decision.
OL,16,FMillions of pensioners are also facing
OL,17,Fa winter with less support after the
OL,18,Fnew Government decided to scrap winter
OL,19,Ffuel payments for those who do not
OL,20,Freceive pension credits or other
OL,21,Fbenefits.
