OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAbout 10 million pensioners will miss
OL,12,Fout on the payments of up to #300 this
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FOctober's price cap will be
OL,16,Fsignificantly lower than during the
OL,17,Fpeak of the energy crisis, which was
OL,18,Ffuelled by Russia's invasion of
OL,19,FUkraine in February 2022, driving up
OL,20,Fcosts in an already-turbulent market.
