OL,3,CHouseholds urged to send in meter
OL,4,Creadings ahead of Oct 1 price hike
OL,6,FHowever, experts think there is likely
OL,7,Fto be a further increase in January,
OL,8,Fwith more rises possible early in the
OL,9,Fnew year due to escalating tensions in
OL,10,Fthe Russia-Ukraine war.
OL,12,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan
OL,13,FBrearley has urged consumers to "shop
OL,14,Faround" and consider a fixed-rate
OL,15,Ftariff that could save money, adding
OL,16,Fthat the regulator was working with
OL,17,FGovernment, suppliers, charities and
OL,18,Fconsumer groups to do "everything we
OL,19,Fcan" to support customers.
