OL,6,FCitizens Advice has said it was
OL,7,Fparticularly concerned about
OL,8,Fhouseholds with children and young
OL,9,Fpeople and those on lower incomes, who
OL,10,Fwere most likely to struggle with
OL,11,Ftheir heating costs.
OL,13,FComparison site Uswitch.com calculated
OL,14,Fthat the average household on an SVT
OL,15,Fis expected to spend #135 on energy in
OL,16,FOctober compared with #55 in September
OL,17,Fdue to a combination of higher rates
OL,18,Fand increased usage at the start of
OL,19,Fautumn.
