OL,6,F"If you delay submitting your
OL,7,Freadings, some of your September
OL,8,Fenergy usage could end up being
OL,9,Festimated and therefore charged under
OL,10,Fthe higher October rates. Try making
OL,11,Fthis task a monthly habit for billing
OL,12,Faccuracy.
OL,14,F"Households are also advised to see
OL,15,Fwhether now is the time to change
OL,16,Ftheir energy tariff, to beat the
OL,17,FOctober price hikes.
